  <name>Mesa Vulkan Drivers with nonfree Video Acceleration support</name>
  <summary>Accelerated Linux Graphics Driver</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      The Mesa Vulkan Drivers provides an interface to video decode
      acceleration and presentation hardware present in AMD graphics
      processing units and/or Intel counterpart running on AMD and/or
      Intel drivers. The drive provides support for H264, AVC and VC-1.
    </p>
